&lt;p&gt;You’re the person who can hold an earnings call and read the fine print in a credit agreement in the same afternoon, and enjoy both. You’ve either been a public-company CFO or you’re the obvious next one, and you’re a little impatient to prove it. You don’t need to be the deepest technical accountant in the building, because we have a strong team for that, but you know what great looks like and you won’t let us get sloppy. You think like an owner, you say the ha

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Grove Collaborative is a sustainability-focused consumer products company creating household and personal care essentials that are effective, beautifully designed, and healthier for people and the planet. We are a certified B Corp, plastic-neutral, and on a mission to transform the CPG industry for good.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;THE ROLE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
