&lt;p&gt;You&#39;ll own replenishment planning across a high-SKU, DTC assortment, managing inventory across two fulfillment centers in a fast-moving eCommerce environment. If you&#39;ve carried this kind of complexity before — large SKU counts, multiple vendors, high velocity — and have used modern planning platforms and AI tooling to manage it at scale rather than through sheer effort, we&#39;d love to hear from you.&lt;/p&gt;
