&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Order Management&lt;/strong&gt; — Track orders from PO submission through EDI confirmation and receipt into fulfillment centers. Recommend stock balance transfers between warehouse locations based on demand signals and fulfillment data.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Continuous Improvement&lt;/strong&gt; — Champion ongoing improvement in planning systems, data quality, and processes. Proactively identify and pilot AI and automation opportunities — anomaly detection, automated reorder triggers, scenario modeling — and share what works with the broader team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
